Class FlightReservationSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • startup.FlightReservationSystem

  • public class FlightReservationSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple flight reservation system whereby passengers can be created, flights created, and passengers booked on the flights. First class passengers are initially given a seat and a meal plan. Regular passengers are booked on a flight with no seat and can later be given a seat.
    Author:
    Matthew Mulenga
